[section#library.c
    [:en] The C standard library
    [:zh_CN] C 标准程序库
]

[para]
[:en]
The [=Cpp] standard library also makes available the facilities of the C
standard library, [% library[!C standard]] suitably adjusted to ensure static
type safety.
[:zh_CN]
[=Cpp] 标准程序库中还可使用 [%程序库 [!C 标准～]] C 标准程序库中的功能，它们已经
经过调整以确保静态类型安全性。

[para]
[:en]
The descriptions of many library functions rely on the C standard library for
the semantics of those functions.
[:zh_CN]
许多库函数的描述依赖于 C 标准程序库中这些函数的语义。

[:en]
In some cases, the signatures specified in this document may be different from
the signatures in the C standard library, and additional overloads may be
declared in this document, but the behavior and the preconditions (including any
preconditions implied by the use of an ISO C [`restrict] qualifier) are the same
unless otherwise stated.
[:zh_CN]
某些情况下，本文档所给出的签名与在 C 标准程序库中的签名有所不同，并且本文档会
提供额外的重载，但其行为和前条件（包括由使用 ISO C 的 [`restrict] 限定符所蕴含的
前条件），除非另有规定，否则都是相同的。

[para]
[:en]
A call to a C standard library function is a non-constant library call
([#defns.nonconst.libcall]) if it raises a floating-point exception other than
[`FE_INEXACT].
[:zh_CN]
对 C 标准程序库函数的调用，若其引发除 [`FE_INEXACT] 之外的浮点异常，则是
非常量库调用（[#defns.nonconst.libcall]）。

[:en]
The semantics of a call to a C standard library function evaluated as a core
constant expression are those specified in Annex F of the C standard[#:fn]
to the extent applicable to the floating-point types ([#basic.fundamental])
that are parameter types of the called function.
[:zh_CN]
作为核心常量表达式而进行求值的 C 标准程序库函数的调用，其语义按照 C 标准的附录 F
的规定[#:fn]，其范围包括所调用函数的形参类型为浮点类型（[#basic.fundamental]）
的情况。

[note:foot]
[:en]
See also ISO/IEC 9899:2018 section 7.6.
[:zh_CN]
另见 ISO/IEC 9899:2008 章节 7.6.
[note:end]

[begin:note]
[:en]
Annex F specifies the conditions under which floating-point exceptions are
raised and the behavior when NaNs and/or infinities are passed as arguments.
[:zh_CN]
附录 F 规定了引发浮点异常的条件，以及以 NaN 和/或无穷值作为实参传递时的行为。
[end:note]

[begin:note]
[:en]
Equivalently, a call to a C standard library function is a non-constant library
call if [`errno] is set when [`math_errhandling & MATH_ERRNO] is [`true].
[:zh_CN]
相同地，当 [`math_errhandling & MATH_ERRNO] 为 [`true] 时，如果对 C 标准程序库
函数的调用设置了 [`errno]，则它是非常量程序库调用。
[end:note]
